column5: Great report and wonderful outing for you and your brother, Andrew, Thanks for that.
Looks like a great weekend to me!
Nothing wrong with a weekend like that.   btw you got any gas?
Yeaaaah buddy! Good shootin' Andrew   I'm even more excited for our upcoming trip in less than 3 weeks!!
looks like it was a good time, thanks for sharing and well done
Nice pike! Hard to beat a couple of fish like that!
Awesome! Did you see any monsters? 45+ inches?
Awesome report. Nice pike you guys got.
nice set of slimers there. well done.
Very nice stuff there....were you strictly using lures or did you try live/dead bait?
Good stuff....heading to Temagami for opener up there, and it will be all lures for us as well
Awesome weekend, looks like a blast!
